2026-04-09 04:40:16,457 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'IIIT-Naya Raipur is a wonderful place for students who wish to pursue their engineering studies. The campus offers a unique blend of fun and studies, providing umpteen opportunities for growth and development in various disciplines. As mentioned by Yash Aavart Pathak, B.Tech (ECE) Student, the college provides a platform where students can learn, experience, and sharpen their skills.\n\nThe curriculum is very good and can be compared with any of the other premier institutes, as shared by Aman Varma, B.Tech (CSE) Student. The college also has a strong focus on cultural, athletic, and educational activities, making it an exciting place to spend four years of your life, as mentioned by Prachi Priyam, B.Tech (CSE) Student.\n\nThe campus is home to supportive seniors and friendly professors who are always willing to help students. The college also organizes various events, workshops, and fests throughout the year, making it a fantastic place to be.'
