2026-04-09 05:33:19,850 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'According to the knowledge base context, the admission process for B.Tech. students at IIIT-NR is as follows:\n\n* The admission to B.Tech programs begins in May-June.\n* Admission to the undergraduate program of the DSPM IIIT-NR is based strictly on the merit of the candidate as inferred from their performance in JEE (Joint Entrance Examination).\n* The minimum eligibility for applying for the B.Tech program under Chhattisgarh quota at IIIT-NR is 50% aggregate marks in Physics and Mathematics (45% for SC/ST/OBC/PWD candidates).\n\nFor admission to its programs under CG Quota, the institute follows the Chhattisgarh State Government policy on reservation of 30% to Women. However, for admission under All India Quota & NTPC, Government of India policy on reservation applies.\n\nThe official email id for any inquiries or details is btech_admissions@iiitnr.ac.in, and phone number is 0771-2474182 (during office hours only).'
