2026-04-09 05:40:18,892 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: "According to the knowledge base context, there is an Opportunity Internship Program (OIP) at IIIT-NR. Here are some details:\n\n* Mode of Carrying out the Internship: Offline only.\n* Eligibility: Students from other reputed institutes pursuing a bachelor's or master's degree are eligible to do an internship in IIIT-NR under the supervision of any faculty member at IIIT-NR.\n* Candidate must be from CSE, IT, ECE, ETE, EE, EEE, EI, Mathematics, Physics, Management, and related backgrounds. B.Tech candidates must be completing their 6th semester (3rd year).\n* Duration: An intern has to work offline for 6 to 8 weeks to receive a stipend and certificate.\n* Stipend will be provided to selected students on successful internship completion and his/her faculty supervisor's recommendation.\n\nYou can find more information about the OIP at IIIT-NR by visiting their official website or contacting them directly."
