2026-04-09 05:52:35,009 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'According to the knowledge base context, here are some details about the fellowship program:\n\n* Fellowship Eligibility: A student cannot avail of two fellowships simultaneously.\n* CMIT M.Tech fellows are permitted to participate in campus placement drives along with other M.Tech students. However, joining any company is only allowed after successful completion of the M.Tech program. Any deviation from this may invoke the bond clause.\n\nAdditionally, here are some specific details about the fellowship:\n\n* AICTE Fellowship: No, a CMIT M.Tech fellow with a valid GATE score cannot receive the AICTE fellowship of ₹12,500 in addition to the CMIT fellowship.\n* Government of Chhattisgarh Sponsorship: The Government of Chhattisgarh sponsors only the tuition fee. Other expenses including hostel accommodation, mess, examination fees, medical insurance, SAC charges, etc., must be borne by the fellows.\n\nPlease note that these are the available details about the fellowship program in the knowledge base. If you have any specific questions or need more information, please feel free to ask!'
