2026-04-15 07:41:25,247 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'IIIT Naya Raipur is a state university established under the International Institute of Information Technology University Act 2013. The institute was established in 2013, and its first academic session commenced from August 2015.\n\nThe institute currently offers two courses - Computer Science and Electronics & Communication Engineering. The admission criteria for these courses are based on JEE Main rank, with an additional eligibility criterion of 50% in Physics and Mathematics (45% for SC/ST students).\n\nStudents at IIIT Naya Raipur have praised the institution for its good learning environment, excellent teachers, labs, library, and infrastructure. They have also appreciated the opportunities to participate in various events, workshops, and fests that take place on campus.\n\nThe institute has a strong focus on innovation and creativity, with programs like SYMPOSIUM 2k16 on Business Intelligence and Big Data Analytics, which provides students with exposure to the big data world. Other initiatives like DARPAN 2k16, a self-introspection workshop, have also been successful in promoting self-confidence, self-awareness, and solid foundations of knowledge among students.\n\nOverall, IIIT Naya Raipur seems to be an excellent institution for engineering aspirants who seek to pursue their career in technology.'
