2026-04-23 14:03:05,941 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'According to the provided information, there is a Training and Placement Cell at DSPM IIIT-Naya Raipur that liaises with prospective recruiters such as industrial establishments and corporate houses which conduct campus interviews and select students from both disciplines. The cell provides infra-structural facilities to conduct group discussions, tests, and interviews, and other logistics required for the same.\n\nAs per the information provided under "Industry" section, IIIT-NR has been established with seed support of NTPC and will actively work with NTPC to develop custom solutions for their needs. The institute is also working with R&D teams at NTPC to understand their needs and engage faculty and students in addressing those needs.\n\nIt seems that the college does not have a specific vocational training program, but rather focuses on providing its students with academic skills as well as physical, behavioral, and societal skills required to be successful team players in the industry.\n\n*Relevant Links:*\n- Companies Visited for Placement: https://www.iiitnr.ac.in/content/companies-visited-2021-25'
