2026-04-23 14:05:39,921 [INFO] [WEBHOOK] Auto-reply sent to +918770441755: 'According to the provided information, IIIT Naya Raipur is pleased to announce a 45-days summer vocational training/internship program in physical mode at IIIT Naya Raipur campus during summer break of 2025. The program aims to enhance the employability and research skills among UG/PG students.\n\nHere are the details about the program:\n\n* Target Audience: B.Tech. (3rd Year and Final Year Students)/M.Tech.\n* Duration: 6-8 Weeks\n* Mode: Physical Mode (Preferable)/Online (Special cases)\n* Enrolment/Registration Fee: 6000/- (Including GST)\n* Enrolment Link: https://forms.gle/BDv5hDYT8bfXQzgy5\n\nThere are four major themes/tracks available for the training program:\n\n1. Data Science Foundation and Application with Python\n2. AI/Machine Learning, Data Science with Python Programming, and Mobile/Web App Development\n3. VLSI and Embedded System Design\n4. Cyber Security and Blockchain Technology\n\nThe registration fee covers course logistics and certification. For accommodation, hostel rooms are available in the campus @Rs50 per day. Canteen/mess is available for fooding on pay and eat basis.\n\nTimelines:\n\n* For VI Sem: May 25, 2025 (Extended deadline)\n* For IV Sem: June 22, 2025 (Extended deadline)\n* Start date for VI Sem students: May 26, 2025\n* Start date for IV Sem students: June 23, 2025\n\n*Relevant Links:*\n- Internship / Outreach Program: https://www.iiitnr.ac.in/content/outreach-2025\n- Vocational Training Programme: https://www.iiitnr.ac.in/content/vocational-training-programme'
